---
title: Crispy Buffalo Tofu Bites with Mac-n-Cheese and Green Beans
description: These buffalo tofu bites are crispy, tasty and full of flavour. Cream cheese is the secret ingredient that makes this mac-n-cheese extra rich and delicious. Both paired with tender-crisp green beans, tonight's 30-minute dinner is a total game changer!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tofu-croustillant-style-buffalo-52ae265b.jpg
